# Dead code false positive patterns.
# Lines starting with '#' are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
# Each line is a pattern (regex for Go, name for Python/JS) to exclude from results.
#
# Common false positives:
# - Entry points (main, init, exported APIs)
# - Reflection-based code
# - Plugin architectures
# - Test helpers
#
# Examples:
# main
# init
# TestMain
